  Right now we have several ongoing groups or individuals working on some great projects - FA camps, raids , webpage, tech advisor, web page research and tips and the Prize Patrol to name but a few. If you want to relieve yourself from all those days, hours and minutes you've been storing you have come to the right place ! For all you fledglings out there that just can't seem to find a newbie  , volunteering is a great way to help out the guild and become a full fledged member. Send an e-mail to debsc@peoplepc.com forthwith, your hand raised high in the air , and I'll put you work ! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
