Numtini may want to create one in Erudin for example to store items from Grimm<br>
and Kaldaori may want to create one in Qeynos. Numtini collects the looted<br>
stuff (armor, weapons , nifty things etc) Kaldaori contacts the crafters <br>
( Sunlar and alts, Varigon, Gaffan , GorteKaymar , Laninie come to mind right away) <br>
by e-mail or a post to the boards and the 2 of you organize the creation of the <br>
packs and different ways to distribute them .  <br>
<br>
  You may want to keep the packs race and class specific. Wicker<br>
is great for druids but not much help to a mage, for example. Think of including<br>
bandages for a warrior perhaps , or snake fangs for a caster and their pets. <br>
Beetle eyes , bone chips, and lightstones are other nice things that many <br>
can use. Something frivilous like a flower or berry is a nice touch. Keep the 'uber'<br>
loot for special occasions and /or contests. Keep the location of the event<br>
in mind and the classes you are most likely to encounter. Work with Gwion <br>
on the way the packs will be given out that day and collection of packs <br>
for distribution that people may have already started or may want to create <br>
themselves for the event. <br>
<br>
 The possibilities here are endless and I think this could be a lot of fun.<br>
<br>
 What do you think? Any other ideas come to mind ?<br>
<br>
